732e696f2f62616467652f706c6174666f726d2d4c696e75782532302537432532306d61634f532d6c69676874677265792e737667\n https://camo.githubusercontent.com/c0127df7f89190bcb4c4a69304fd0d798dac9cb495a2f4ff876d9c65ca062a9d/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f62616467652f707974686f6e2d332e31302b2d677265656e2e737667\n https://camo.githubusercontent.com/d31df35bff072f104a0e03fd591b222170121a52d1cd93ac9c5c51d06aec7bfc/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f62616467652f4d43502d636f6d70617469626c652d707572706c652e737667\n\nAI-powered toolkit for Xiaohongshu (小红书 / RedNote) that turns your favorite posts into AI memory.\n\n- MCP Integration — Search, browse, comment via AI assistants\n\n- Trend Tracking — Auto-generate topic reports with engagement analytics\n\n- Memory Export — Convert your liked/saved posts into AI-searchable knowledge base\n\nBuilt on [xiaohongshu-mcp](https://github.com/xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp) and [XHS-Downloader](https://github.com/JoeanAmier/XHS-Downloader).\n\nFeature\nDescription\n\nSearch\nSearch posts by keywords\n\nFeed\nGet homepage recommendations\n\nPost Details\nFetch post content, comments, engagement stats\n\nComment\nPost comments to notes\n\nUser Profile\nGet user info and their posts\n\nTrend Tracking\nAuto-generate topic analysis reports\n\nLong Image Export\nExport posts as annotated JPG long images\n\nMemory Export\nExport liked/saved posts as Markdown for AI memory\n\nDownload from [GitHub Releases](https://github.com/xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp/releases):\n\n# Linux x64\nwget https://github.com/xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp/releases/latest/download/xiaohongshu-mcp-linux-amd64.tar.gz\nwget https://github.com/xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp/releases/latest/download/xiaohongshu-login-linux-amd64.tar.gz\n\n# macOS ARM\nwget https://github.com/xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp/re\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b8fd9721045128a6\">>>"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772420666742}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae7d597e","parentId":"649cd434","timestamp":"2026-03-02T03:04:38.827Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我获取到了这些 GitHub 仓库的信息。现在让我整理一下，为用户展示一个清晰的列表和介绍。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好的，老板！这是你要的 OpenClaw Skills 列表和介绍：\n\n---\n\n## 📦 OpenClaw Skills 列表\n\n| # | 仓库 | 技能名称 | 用途 |\n|---|------|----------|------|\n| 1 | `web-infra-dev/midscene-skills` | `desktop-computer-automation` | 🖥️ **桌面自动化** - 基于 Midscene.js 的视觉驱动桌面控制，支持 macOS/Windows/Linux，可点击、打字、截图、启动应用等，无需 DOM 或无障碍标签 |\n| 2 | `adisinghstudent/easyclaw` | `openclaw-config` | 🔧 **OpenClaw 配置管理** - 完整的 OpenClaw 参考手册，包含文件映射、会话搜索、日志分析、Cron 调试、渠道状态检查、故障排除指南等 |\n| 3 | `sundial-org/awesome-openclaw-skills` | `exa-web-search-free` | 🔍 **免费 Web 搜索** - 提供免费的网络搜索功能（基于 Exa API），用于快速查找信息 |\n| 4 | `useai-pro/openclaw-skills-security` | `skill-vetter` | 🛡️ **技能安全审核** - 安全优先的技能审核工具，可检测恶意技能（ typo 攻击、权限滥用、提示注入、数据外泄等），返回 SAFE/SUSPICIOUS/DANGEROUS/BLOCK 评级 |\n| 5 | `zhjiang22/openclaw-xhs` | `xiaohongshu` | 📕 **小红书集成** - MCP 集成的小红书工具包，支持搜索帖子、获取推荐、查看评论、用户资料、趋势追踪、记忆导出等功能 |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 快速安装命令\n\n```bash\n# 安装单个技能\nnpx skills add web-infra-dev/midscene-skills@desktop-computer-automation\nnpx skills add adisinghstudent/easyclaw@openclaw-config\nnpx skills add sundial-org/awesome-openclaw-skills@exa-web-search-free\nnpx skills add useai-pro/openclaw-skills-security@skill-vetter\nnpx skills add zhjiang22/openclaw-xhs@xiaohongshu\n\n# 或批量安装\nnpx skills add web-infra-dev/midscene-skills\nnpx skills add adisinghstudent/easyclaw\nnpx skills add sundial-org/awesome-openclaw-skills\nnpx skills add useai-pro/openclaw-skills-security\nnpx skills add zhjiang22/openclaw-xhs\n```\n\n---\n\n## 💡 推荐用途\n\n- **桌面自动化** → 需要控制电脑操作时（点击、打字、截图）\n- **配置管理** → 调试 OpenClaw 问题或查找配置信息\n- **Web 搜索** → 需要联网查资料时\n- **安全审核** → 安装新技能前先审核安全性\n- **小红书** → 需要分析小红书内容或导出个人数据\n\n需要我帮你安装其中某个技能吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":23702,"output":735,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24437,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772420666751}}
