{"type":"message","id":"22ddab65","parentId":"49dcbcc5","timestamp":"2026-03-02T03:13:28.341Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The midscene computer skill requires model configuration (API key, model name, base URL, etc.) but there's no .env file set up. I need to inform the user about this requirement.\n\nLooking at the SKILL.md, it needs:\n- MIDSCENE_MODEL_API_KEY\n- MIDSCENE_MODEL_NAME\n- MIDSCENE_MODEL_BASE_URL\n- MIDSCENE_MODEL_FAMILY\n\nI should ask the user to configure these or check if there's a global configuration somewhere.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 老板，Midscene 桌面自动化需要配置视觉模型才能工作！\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 缺少模型配置\n\nMidscene 需要以下环境变量（任一即可）：\n\n### 方案 1: Gemini（推荐，免费额度）\n```bash\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_API_KEY=\"你的 Google API Key\"\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_NAME=\"gemini-3-flash\"\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_BASE_URL=\"https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/openai/\"\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_FAMILY=\"gemini\"\n```\n\n### 方案 2: Qwen3-VL（阿里云）\n```bash\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_API_KEY=\"你的 OpenRouter/阿里云 API Key\"\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_NAME=\"qwen/qwen3-vl-235b-a22b-instruct\"\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_BASE_URL=\"https://openrouter.ai/api/v1\"\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_FAMILY=\"qwen3-vl\"\n```\n\n### 方案 3: 豆包 Seed 1.6（火山引擎）\n```bash\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_API_KEY=\"你的豆包 API Key\"\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_NAME=\"doubao-seed-1-6-250615\"\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_BASE_URL=\"https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3\"\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_FAMILY=\"doubao-vision\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 配置方法\n\n在工作空间创建 `.env` 文件：\n```bash\n# 路径：C:\\Users\\14015\\.openclaw\\workspace\\.env\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_API_KEY=\"你的 API Key\"\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_NAME=\"模型名称\"\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_BASE_URL=\"https://...\"\nMIDSCENE_MODEL_FAMILY=\"模型系列\"\n```\n\n---\n\n老板你有哪个模型的 API Key 吗？或者我帮你用 **浏览器扩展方式** 来打开百度搜索天气？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":32347,"output":649,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32996,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRea