{"type":"message","id":"402e0668","parentId":"19f69da8","timestamp":"2026-03-02T03:14:27.729Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板连续发了两个\"？\"，可能是在表达疑惑或者不耐烦。让我更直接一点，用最简单的方式帮他完成任务。\n\n既然桌面自动化需要 API Key 配置比较复杂，我直接用 browser 工具（需要 Chrome 扩展连接）或者直接用 web_search/web_fetch 来查天气。\n\n但 web_search 需要 Brave API Key，之前试过了没有。\n\n最简单的方式：直接用 browser 工具打开百度，但需要老板先连接 Chrome 扩展。\n\n或者我可以直接用 web_fetch 抓取天气网站的内容？\n\n让我换个思路 - 直接用 web_fetch 抓取天气网站，不需要任何配置！\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 老板抱歉，我直接帮你查！\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1008a3ebeae746d19926396d","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://m.weather.com.cn/weather1d/101270101.shtml","maxChars":5000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":33367,"output":331,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33698,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772421260252}}
